ent-RMCBaseballBat-name = wooden baseball bat
ent-RMCBaseballBat-desc = A large wooden baseball bat. Commonly used in colony recreation, but also used as a means of self defense. Often carried by thugs and ruffians.
ent-RMCBaseballBatMetal-name = metal baseball bat
ent-RMCBaseballBatMetal-desc = A large metal baseball bat. Compared to its wooden cousin, the metal bat offers a bit more more force. Often carried by thugs and ruffians.
